{
  "stem": "3638.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could survive, like I said, to the end of the war, if they wouldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we could alwa-- being in the same place, you could always help yourself somehow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, we went to Velichka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from Velichka, you could not carry all the things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the only thing which we carried is the money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The money and gold and jewelry, which my father still had it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was converted in Velichka into the food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We lived from it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Jewish reaction was that-- that-- that it's not going to be good under the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that they-- all the time, they want something else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not satisfied only with confiscated your produce.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later they want furs because the-- the war started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were preparing the war against Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody had to give the furs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're not allowed to have any furs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know, before the war, the Jewish people had a lot of furs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The families, the mother and the sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everything has to be taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the jewelry has to be-- everything has to-- you had to give it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We give some of it, not-- not all of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When did they start asking for this materials, the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, straight, maybe a month or six weeks after.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So already in October, November of '39.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They demanded things, you see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As much as they could, you know, as much as they could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where they didn't cooperate-- I mean, with the furs, they had to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew-- there was a big pile, you know, was a pile as maybe 10-- 10 story pile of furs where they collected.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then later they converted into for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
